        <p><strong>The 15.3% SE tax rate is confirmed for 2026.</strong> The Social Security wage base (~$180,400) is a projection. Official figure confirmed by SSA in October 2026. For your 2025 return, see the <a href="/self-employment-tax-rate-2025">confirmed 2025 SE tax rate page</a>.</p>
